<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٣٠ ... سُورَةُ الرُّومِ ... آياتها ٦٠ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غُلِبَتِ الرُّومُ}</span> ... هَزَمَتْ فَارِسُ الرُّومَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَدْنَى الْأَرْضِ}</span> ... أَقْرَبِ أَرْضِ الشَّامِ إِلَى فَارِسَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَلَبِهِمْ}</span> ... كَوْنِهِمْ مَغْلُوبِينَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِضْعِ سِنِينَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> البِضْعُ:</span> مُدَّةٌ لَا تَزِيدُ عَلَى عَشْرِ سَنَوَاتٍ، وَلَا تَنْقُصُ عَنْ ثَلَاثٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَجَلٍ مُّسَمًّى}</span> ... وَقْتٍ مُقَدَّرٍ تَنْتَهِي إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَثَارُوا}</span> ... حَرَثُوا وَزَرَعُوا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السُّوأَى}</span> ... العُقُوبَةُ المُتَنَاهِيَةُ فيِ السُّوءِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُبْلِسُ}</span> ... يَيْئَسُ مِنَ النَّجَاةِ مِنَ العَذَابِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُحْبَرُونَ}</span> ... يُكْرَمُونَ، وَيُنَعَّمُونَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُحْضَرُونَ}</span> ... مُقِيمُونَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُظْهِرُونَ}</span> ... تَدْخُلُونَ وَقْتَ الظَّهِيرَةِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِّلْعَالِمِينَ}</span> ... جَمْعُ عَالِم، وَهُمْ ذَوُو العِلْمِ وَالبَصِيرَةِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَابْتِغَاؤُكُم مِّن فَضْلِهِ}</span> ... طَلَبُكُمْ لِلرِّزْقِ فيِ النَّهَارِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَوْفًا وَطَمَعًا}</span> ... تَخَافُونَ مِنَ الصَّوَاعِقِ، وَتَطْمَعُونَ فيِ الغَيْثِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَانِتُونَ}</span> ... مُطِيعُونَ مُنْقَادُونَ لِأَمْرِهِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>